OL,5, Two days before Christmas, TikTok      
OL,6, called London-based journalist Cristina
OL,7, Criddle to tell her two of its         
OL,8, employees in China, and two in the US, 
OL,9, had viewed user data from her personal 
OL,10, account without her knowledge or       
OL,11, consent.                               
OL,13,F"It was just really chilling and       
OL,14,Fhorrible and, personally, quite        
OL,15,Fviolating," she says.                  
OL,17,F"I was at my family home with my       
OL,18,Fteenage sister, teenage cousins - and  
OL,19,Fthey all use TikTok all of the time.   
OL,20,FThey were like, 'Whoa, should we be    
OL,21,Fworried?'".                            
